Recursively Find Sum of First N Even Numbers | Implement a recursive function to compute the sum of first N even numbers.

import java.util.*;
class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        System.out.println(recursiveEvenNumbers(n));
    }
    public static int recursiveEvenNumbers(int n){
        if(n==0) return 0;
        return 2 * n+recursiveEvenNumbers(n-1);
    }
}

output:
5
30
